{"tid":1431510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【升級方向】午餐？罷了","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:40:11.000Z","uid":273621,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"44f3ad198338a91ec3cd8c21732e070147c174c8","tid":1431510,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"首先sorry for 上個post 1999<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429165</a><br />\n<br />\n禁食既意思唔係靠自己唔食野去威脅政府，<br />\n而係靠午餐時段<strong>唔去食肆消費</strong>黎威脅政府。<br />\n<br />\n個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>罷</strong></span>字既意義就係平時做既野今日唔做。<br />\n因為政府可以用槍指住我停止我遊行，但唔通可以用槍指住我逼我食飯咩？呢樣先係不合作運動既威力。<br />\n<br />\n今日取消左既海港城罷買（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430270</a>) 正正就係做唔到個罷字既精髓。平時都唔行海港城，今日去行唔係做少左野，而係做多左野。<br />\n<br />\n罷買午餐唔一定要唔食，其實帶飯唔出去食都得。不過直頭食都唔食會比較有noise，行動自帶宣傳效果。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以考慮下，黎緊星期一<br />\n812一齊禁食"},{"pid":"0e067c851fdff86a9aea993e1e02f7eb796658ac","tid":1431510,"uid":273621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"手足願意為我擋子彈<br />\n我願意為你地捱肚餓"},{"pid":"4d161f165d0aaebcc100e644eb0465a66c1ecd33","tid":1431510,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"[突發] 更新後熱門功能缺陷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431451</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9231eec237bd7ed0309c9be62172f678fead288","tid":1431510,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"手足願意為我擋子彈<br />\n我願意為你地捱肚餓"},{"pid":"40f0349e7b02e35afa8719432e69c1873f09af1b","tid":1431510,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:25:38.000Z","msg":"最易罷買既就係自己份午餐"},{"pid":"2e9382d61f783d6d1525a4d47de28f647a13ff9f","tid":1431510,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4